OL,6,FAround 100 fewer people were killed or
OL,7,Fseriously injured on 20mph and 30mph
OL,8,Froads in the 12 months after the 20mph
OL,9,Fdefault speed limit was introduced,
OL,10,Fcompared to the same period a year
OL,11,Fbefore.
