OL,3,CFewer collisions and casualties since
OL,4,Cdefault 20mph changes
OL,6,FThe Welsh Conservatives are urging a
OL,7,Fmore targeted approach, focusing on
OL,8,Fsensitive areas like schools and
OL,9,Fhospitals, rather than a what it calls
OL,10,Fa 'blanket' 20mph limit.
OL,12,FThey believe the current default
OL,13,Fapproach has caused "confusion and
OL,14,Ffrustration for drivers" and advocate
OL,15,Ffor scrapping the default 20mph limit
OL,16,Fand introducing it only where needed.
OL,18,FWill the Welsh Government change
OL,19,Fcourse?
