OL,6,FThe Welsh Government appears committed
OL,7,Fto its current policy with the Cabinet
OL,8,FSecretary for Transport and North
OL,9,FWales, Ken Skates, stating the
OL,10,Fgovernment is aware there is still "a
OL,11,Fway to go" to see the full impact of
OL,12,Fthe policy.
OL,14,FHe noted the government has "listened
OL,15,Fto people on the policy" and has
OL,16,Fempowered local authorities to make
OL,17,Fchanges where it is safe to do so.
